          <h4 class="text-base font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-900">How Your Rank is Determined</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Your rank within your chosen category is based on how much you contribute. The more you contribute, the higher your rank. However, the amounts remain private, adding mystery and excitement to the competition.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
          <h4 class="text-base font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-900">When Your Credit Appears</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            After your payment is confirmed, your credit will be posted within 12 hours. We work hard to ensure everyone's contributions are recognized promptly. If there's a delay, we'll keep you informed.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
          <h4 class="text-base font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-900">Handling Chargebacks</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            If a chargeback occurs, your credit will be immediately removed and you'll be blocked from future participation. We do this to protect the integrity of the rankings and ensure fairness for all contributors.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
          <h4 class="text-base font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-900">Updating Your Listing or Link</h4>
